name: Dirk Blast
description:
This photograph was one of the offical images used as promotional material for Dirk Verbeuren, taken by Hannah Verbeuren.

All rights reserved, copyrights remain with Hannah Verbeuren.

This image is an unframed, unmatted, full-bleed (does not show borders or white space) print.

Glossy finish unless otherwise indicated.  

Each print is developed in a photo lab catering to professional photographers equipped with the finest photo finishing equipment on the highest quality photographic paper with accurate color and realistic saturation. 

There are no refunds for a purchase. 
If your purchase has been damaged in shipment, you may exchange your product for an exact replacement (minus shipping costs) up to 14 days after you have received your purchase. You will be responsible for returning items in their original condition as well as return shipping costs.

The logo will not be printed on the image.

NOTE: Autographed purchases will be signed by hand on the image itself (front) with permanent ink.
